"  Dressing:","1/3 cup seedless green grapes","1 tablespoon Champagne or white wine vinegar","1 teaspoon olive oil","3/4 teaspoon Dijon mustard","1/2 teaspoon minced fresh Vidalia or sweet onion (optional)","1/8 teaspoon salt","  Dash of white pepper","  Salad:","3/4 pound large shrimp, peeled and deveined","1/2 cup diagonally cut celery","5 cups trimmed arugula","1 cup seedless red grapes, halved","1 cup seedless green grapes, halved","1/4 cup fresh basil leaves, thinly sliced","2 tablespoons crumbled Gorgonzola cheese","1 tablespoon coarsely chopped walnuts, lightly toasted"